<HEADLINE> Flyers Reacquire Winger Jody Hull </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	PHILADELPHIA (AP) -- The Flyers acquired right wing Jody Hull  
from the Atlanta Thrashers on Friday, hoping he will help the 
winless Philadelphia team defend leads and kill penalties, team 
officials said. 
</P>
<P>
	Hull, 30, registered 14 points and 12 penalty minutes in 72  
games for the Flyers last season. 
</P>
